extendedInfo.description: Feel the rush of the stickman challenge! Do you love stickman games? Run to the moon in this new adventure made just for you!Sprint, slide, jump and double jump your way through the most bizarre obstacles in 2.5D stickman has encountered yet!* Brilliant 2.5D level designs!* Running, jumping, ducking and more!* Game Center LeaderboardsCompete for the top score TODAY!This line runner will skate down the blocks, jump like a ninja on a bmx over the extreme obstacles and paper doodle it on the home run! Arcade style skills game with mega reflexes and 3d to boot! Doodle or scribble is less advanced than this game!
